GSTREAMER
---------

Launch a player with the image taken from the webcam

 $ gst-launch v4l2src ! ffmpegcolorspace ! xvimagesink

http://luisbg.blogalia.com/historias/61887
http://www.jonobacon.org/2006/08/28/getting-started-with-gstreamer-with-python/

Pipeline dumps
● Dump pipelines as graphviz graphs
● Use dot to render them
● Run apps with:
GST_DEBUG_DUMP_DOT_DIR=$PWD ./myapp

Logging
● Powerful logging subsystem
● Level, categories, ...
● Run apps with:
GST_DEBUG="*:2,GST_CAPS:4" ./myapp

